paragraphs.title: Import Data (PySpark RDD to SQL/Dataframe)
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

rdd    = sc.textFile("hdfs://sandbox.hortonworks.com:8020/tmp/airlines.csv") \
            .map(lambda x: x.split(","))

header = rdd.take(1)

df     = rdd.filter(lambda x: x!=header[0]) \
            .toDF(header[0])

df.show(5)
print type(df)

paragraphs.title: Import Data (PySpark SQL/Dataframe)
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

df = sqlContext                                 \
    .read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv")    \
    .option("header", "true")                   \
    .option("inferschema", "true")              \
    .option("mode", "DROPMALFORMED")            \
    .load("hdfs://sandbox.hortonworks.com:8020/tmp/airlines.csv")

df.show(5)
print type(df)
